articles.title: Lungo 1.7.0 - Prevent your Mac from sleeping. (Commercial)
articles.description:
Lungo prevents your Mac from falling asleep and your screen from dimming. Lungo can be useful when:
  • Doing a presentation at work
  • Watching YouTube videos in non-fullscreen mode
  • Reading a long article without scrolling
